  "remarks": "Previously listed under UNSC Resolution 2231 – Charter of the United Nations (Sanctions—Iran) Regulation 2016 [F2016L01181]\n\nA subordinate entity of the Aerospace Industries Organisation (AIO). Produces ballistic missiles for Iran. Mehrdada Akhlaghi KETABACHI is the last known head of SBIG.; Listing: Instrument of first designation: Autonomous Sanctions (Designated Persons and Entities and Declared Persons – Iran) Amendment (No. 2) Instrument 2023",
